ExecDesc.value: Winamp MP4 File Parsing Buffer Overflow Vulnerability (IPv6 Version)

EngDesc.value: This threat uses a malicious mp4 media file that once played in a vulnerable Winamp client will result in a denial of service condition or execution of arbitrary code. Winamp is a client application that can retrieve mp4 files from a web server listening on port 80. (IPv6 Version)
